                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Given that a bunch of <m>Sukuma</m> <m>wiki</m> goes for <m>10</m> shillings, a <m>gorogoro</m> of maize for <m>50</m> shillings and a tomamto for <m>5</m> shillings, find the total amount paid by the customer for all the goods.
